            <div data-hf-id="hf-mwcu" class="q">
              The restaurant bill is $<span data-hf-id="hf-0uca" class="jp-mini" id="tip-bill">150</span>. I want to leave a <span data-hf-id="hf-oxkh" class="jp-mini" id="tip-pct">10</span>% tip...
